'''贾里德·休斯'''（{{lang-en|Jarryd Hughes}}，{{bd|1995年|5月21日||}}）生于新南威尔士州悉尼，是一名澳大利亚男子单板滑雪运动员，主攻越野项目<ref name="owia">{{cite web|title=Jarryd Hughes|url=http://www.owia.org/jarryd-hughes.html|work=Olympic Winter Institute of Australia|accessdate=2018-02-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517160856/https://www.owia.org/jarryd-hughes.html|archivedate=2020-05-17}}</ref>。他于2001年在一场校际比赛期间开始接触单板滑雪，当时他的父母在他未滑过单板滑雪的情况下替他报名参加该比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/snowboard/athlete-profile-n3015539-jarryd-hughes.htm|title=Snowboard {{!}} Athlete Profile: Jarryd HUGHES|work=Pyeongchang 2018|accessdate=2020-07-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421135900/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/snowboard/athlete-profile-n3015539-jarryd-hughes.htm|archivedate=2018-04-21}}</ref>。2012年2月，他在加拿大完成了个人的世界杯分站赛首秀<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pickstar.com.au/our-stars/3272/jarryd-hughes|title=Jarryd Hughes|work=PickStar|accessdate=2020-07-19|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200719042438/https://pickstar.com.au/our-stars/3272/jarryd-hughes|archivedate=2020-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年，他在世界极限运动会上获得男子单板滑雪越野项目冠军，成为历史上首位在世界极限运动会上摘金的澳大利亚男选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nswis.com.au/nswis-news/x-games-gold-fuelling-jarryd-hughes-hunger-for-olympic-glory/|title=X-Games gold fuelling Jarryd Hughes' hunger for Olympic glory|work=NSWIS|date=2016-09-27|accessdate=2020-07-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422105309/https://www.nswis.com.au/nswis-news/x-games-gold-fuelling-jarryd-hughes-hunger-for-olympic-glory/|archivedate=2019-04-22}}</ref>。

